high_descs: Move forward and face the stove in front of you.
Take the apple from the counter in front of you.
Face the sink to your right.
Place the apple in the sink in front of you.
Take the knife by the sink in front of you.
Cut the apple in the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Take an apple slice from the sink in front of you.
Face the microwave on your left.
Heat the apple in the microwave, take it out and close the microwave.
Face the sink on your right.
Place the apple slice in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm apple slice in the sink.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove
Pick up the apple on the counter
Turn right and go to the sink
Put the apple in the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter
Cut the apple in the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Pick up an apple piece from the sink
Turn left to the microwave
Put the apple piece in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the apple piece from the microwave
Turn right to the sink
Put the apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, cook a piece of it

high_descs: Go right, then turn left and go to the stove.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn right and go to he sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left of the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink.
Put the knife in the center of the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the slice of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of apple in the sink.
